---
import Rocket from "@/assets/images/rocket.webp";
import Star from "@/assets/icons/star40x40.svg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="mission-section w-full mx-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto py-10 lg:py-20">
    <h1
      class="mission-title text-[min(10vw,72px)] opacity-0 text-center lg:text-left font-playfair text-smokyBlack tracking-tight"
    >
      Nuestra Misión:
    </h1>
    <div
      class="mission-container flex flex-col items-center justify-center lg:flex-row"
    >
      <div>
        <h1
          class="mission-subtitle text-[min(7vw,42px)] mb-4 opacity-0 text-center lg:text-left font-playfair px-2 text-smokyBlack tracking-tight"
        >
          Ayudarte a brillar con propósito
        </h1>
        <div class="mission-text opacity-0">
          <p
            class="text-[min(10vw,18px)] text-center lg:text-left px-2 md:px-0 font-openSans text-smokyBlack mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
          >
            Creemos, basados en nuestra fe, que cada persona tiene una luz y un
            don únicos para poner al servicio de los demás. <span
              class="font-bold italic text-deepplum">Nuestra misión</span
            > darte la claridad estratégica y las herramientas tecnológicas para
            que compartas esa luz sin miedo, sin vender humo y sin sacrificar tu
            esencia.
            <span class="font-bold italic text-deepplum block">
              Brillar no es gritar; es ser auténtico, útil y excelente.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mission-image relative items-center justify-center w-1/2 hidden lg:flex opacity-0"
      >
        <!-- Random positioned stars -->
        <Star class="absolute top-16 left-20 animate-pulse" />
        <Star class="absolute top-32 right-16 animate-pulse delay-300" />
        <Star class="absolute bottom-24 left-12 animate-pulse delay-700" />
        <Star class="absolute bottom-16 right-24 animate-pulse delay-500" />
        <Star class="absolute bottom-32 right-12 animate-pulse delay-400" />
        <Star class="absolute bottom-42 left-24 animate-pulse delay-400" />

        <!-- Rocket -->
        <Image
          id="rocket"
          src={Rocket}
          alt="Rocket"
          height={350}
          width={350}
          class="relative z-10"
        />
        <div id="rocket-path">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 500 500">
            <path
              style="fill: none;"
              d="M 0 500 C 59.433 500 268.622 44.037 500 0"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { aboutMissionAnimation } from "@/utils/scripts/perPageAnimations/about/aboutMissionAnimation";

  document.removeEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", aboutMissionAnimation);
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", aboutMissionAnimation);
</script>
